0/03/horario-verano.png" rel="lightbox[7570]"><img src="http://ayudawordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/horario-verano-499x57.png" alt=""  width="499" height="57" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-7571" /></a></p>\n\n\n\n¿Te gustó este post? ¡Compártelo!\n\n\n	<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://bitacoras.com/anotaciones/http%3A%2F%2Fayudawordpress.com%2Fcambiar-la-hora-en-wordpress-2%2F" title="Bitacoras.com"><img src="http://ayudawordpress.com/wp-content/plugins/sociable/images/bitacoras.png" title="Bitacoras.com" alt="Bitacoras.com" class="sociable-hovers" /></a>\n	<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://twitter.com/home?status=http%3A%2F%2Fayudawordpress.com%2Fcambiar-la-hora-en-wordpress-2%2F" title="TwitThis"><img src="http://ayudawordpress.com/wp-content/plugins/sociable/images/twitter.png" title="TwitThis" alt="TwitThis" class="sociable-hovers" /></a>\n	<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fayudawordpress.com%2Fcambiar-la-hora-en-wordpress-2%2F&amp;t=Cambiar%20la%20hora%20en%20WordPress" title="Facebook"><img src="http://ayudawordpress.com/wp-content/plugins/sociable/images/facebook.png" title="Facebook" alt="Facebook" class="sociable-hovers" /></a>\n	<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://meneame.net/submit.php?url=http%3A%2F%2Fayudawordpress.com%2Fcambiar-la-hora-en-wordpress-2%2F" title="Meneame"><img src="http://ayudawordpress.com/wp-content/plugins/sociable/images/meneame.png" title="Meneame" alt="Meneame" class="sociable-hovers" /></a>\n	<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.google.com/bookmarks/mark?op=edit&amp;bkmk=http%3A%2F%2Fayudawordpress.com%2Fcambiar-la-hora-en-wordpress-2%2F&amp;title=Cambiar%20la%20hora%20en%20WordPress&amp;annotation=Si%20vives%20en%20alg%C3%BAn%20pa%C3%ADs%20en%20el%20que%20cambien%20la%20hora%20en%20Verano%20e%20Invierno%20hoy%20seguramente%20andar%C3%A1s%20como%20yo%2C%20un%20poco%20descolocado.%20Pues%20bien%2C%20y%20no%2